                                                                        "tournamentId": "",
                                                                        "title": "",
                                                                        "body": "Earned his fourth career PGA TOUR win at the AT\u0026T Pebble Beach Pro-Am and advanced to the TOUR Championship for the fifth time, finishing the season No. 11 in the FedExCup standings. Marked his sixth season qualifying for the FedExCup Playoffs. Recorded eight top-10s, his first time earning more than seven in a season, and made the cut in 21 of 23 starts. Compiled 26 consecutive par-or-better scores (R1, THE CJ CUP @ SHADOW CREEK through R4, AT\u0026T Pebble Beach Pro-Am), tied for the longest streak of the season on TOUR. Following the TOUR Championship, was selected as a captain's pick to represent the United States at the Ryder Cup, marking his first appearance at the event."
