                                                                                "title": "",
                                                                                "body": "Finished No. 100 in the 2024 FedExCup Fall standings after posting two top-10 finishes in 27 starts, including a T2 finish in the final event of the FedExCup Fall at The RSM Classic, which elevated him from No. 127 to No. 100 in the standings to secure fully-exempt status on TOUR in 2025."
