                                                                                "tournamentId": "",
                                                                                "title": "",
                                                                                "body": "Qualified for the FedExCup Playoffs for the third consecutive season and seventh total, finishing No. 91 in the official FedExCup standings, but was limited to 12 starts due to a back injury. Did not compete after missing the cut at the U.S. Open, missing the final two months of the season. Recorded three top-fives in his 12 starts, highlighted by a fourth-place result at The Honda Classic, and made nine cuts."
